The srand and rand functions are available from avr-libc, but the problem is getting a good seed for the random,
hopefully one that is different each time the board is booted.

Important reading material:
    http://maxembedded.com/2011/06/avr-basics/
    http://maxembedded.com/2011/06/port-operations-in-avr/
    http://maxembedded.com/2011/06/the-adc-of-the-avr/
